    "body": "Problem:\r\n`aucmd_restbuf` must be guarded in case `aucmd_prepbuf` wasn't called.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nUpdate `aucmd_restbuf` to be a no-op if `aucmd_prepbuf` wasn't called. This requires `aco` to be zero-initialized.\r\n\r\n",
